---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative mt-32 border-t border-white/[0.08] py-16 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Glow orb subtle -->
  <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-vivid w-[500px] h-[500px] -top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 opacity-30"></div>

  <div class="container-wide relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <a href="https://gang4.io" class="inline-block mb-4">
        <img
          src="/logo-gang4.svg"
          alt="Gang4"
          class="h-9 w-auto hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/60 max-w-md leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-white">Scalez votre whitelisting Meta en un clic.</strong><br />
        Pour les DNVB françaises qui dépassent <span class="text-gang4-vivid">30k€/mois</span> sur Meta Ads.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">Navigation</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/60">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Accueil</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Tous les articles</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://gang4.io/whitelisting" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Solution Whitelisting</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://gang4.io/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Site principal →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">Légal</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/60">
        <li><a href="https://gang4.io/mentions-legales" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Mentions légales</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://gang4.io/cgv" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CGV</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-wide relative z-10 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/[0.08] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <div class="text-xs text-white/40">
      © {year} Gang4 SAS · Tous droits réservés
    </div>
    <div class="text-xs text-white/40">
      Édité depuis Paris, propulsé par <a href="https://gang4.io" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white">Gang4</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
